file.name: expected_auth_with_named_schemes.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fruits
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /secure/bearer:
    get:
      operationId: getSecureBearer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      security:
        - secBearer: []
  /secure/basic:
    get:
      operationId: getSecureBasic
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      security:
        - secBasic: []
  /secure/apiKeyHeader:
    get:
      operationId: getSecureApikeyheader
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      security:
        - secApiKeyHeader: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    secApiKeyHeader:
      type: apiKey
      name: apikey
      in: header
    secBasic:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
    secBearer:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer

Error: notImplemented: path "/secure/basic": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
